snippet.title: Thamma Official Trailer | Ayushmann, Rashmika, Paresh, Nawazuddin | In Cinemas This Diwali- 21st Oct
snippet.description:
A forgotten legend from our folklore, #Thamma takes centre stage this Diwali!

Maddock Horror Comedy Universe presents a bloody love story, produced by Dinesh Vijan & Amar Kaushik and directed by Aditya Sarpotdar. In cinemas worldwide on 21st October.

#Thamma #ThammaThisDiwali #ThammaOn21stOct
#ThammaTrailerOut now

Maddock Films presents #Thamma 

In Cinemas on 21st October.

snippet.title: HAQ | Official Teaser | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Shazia Bano takes her husband Abbas to court after he abandons her and their children, sparking a national battle over faith, women‚Äôs rights, and justice. Inspired by the landmark Supreme Court judgement of Mohd. Ahmed Khan vs. Shah Bano Begum. Haq is the story of one woman‚Äôs fight for her rights and justice. 

Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

HAQ is a fictionalized and dramatized version of events stated in the book titled ‚ÄòBano: Bharat ki Beti‚Äô written¬†by¬†Jigna¬†Vora.

Cast- Yami Gautam, Emraan Hashmi, Vartika Singh, Danish Husain, Sheeba Chadha,

Kokaina
Tu hai bandi ghalat
De kaya palat
mohol badalati hai kaise

Buri aafat tu
Buri aadat tu
Mujhe hit karti hai jaise

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)
Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina

Yeh pareshan karegi 
Leke jaan rahegi
Bada nuksaan karegi
Aaj koi kaand karegi

Tu hi hai alpha tu hi hai beta
Galt jo dekhe tujhe
Tujhe tod du gita 
saanvle rang ki nagin jaisi
Hit karti hai jaise chitta

Aaju baaju na koi fatakra 
Launda koi na palk jhapakra
Tar tar tar hai Paseena tapakra
Vo bhi ni hatri mai bhi ni hatra 

Tak tak tina
Sun o Haseena
Kamar ghuma
aane de paseena
Aapka scene me tod na koi
game me apna bhi tod koi na

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Mere Nal Behnde Jehde Sare Bande Main..

Jado Boldi Main, Bullan Cho Barood Girda..

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: Sushant Ghimire - Chitthi (the last letter) | Prod. AVSHK | Official Release | Nahunu ae nirasha
snippet.description:
Wanted to express some words on behalf of those braves who lost their lives in Genz protest. Wherever they are , they might miss home , miss their friends/family , miss everything about being alive . Hope they rest in peace and justice be prevail.

 Chitthi- The last letter ,is a tribute to all of them .

Composed/ Written and Performed by : Sushant Ghimire
Audio Produced by : AVSHK
Mix/Mastered : AVSHK
Recorded at : Esther's Production
Bass Guitar: Dura Himself
Sarod: Sushant Ghimire
Alaap: Rupesh Jha
Back vox: Kaizen , Dura, Rupesh, Sushant.
Artwork : Praeev Shrestha/ Anmol Adhikari

Special Thanks: 
Rijan Maharjan, Bhisma Raj Ghimire.

Lyrics:
Awaz mera gunjiyeki, mai taadhi jaana le
Ki barsau ka yaad ti birsinchau ki, mai chaadi jana le
Chamki rahula ma tara jhai timra
Sparsha chann mera tyahi wari pari
Timro angalo Jhai nyano navayepani
Herirahula ma chamkine gari.... Ma chamkine gari

Baat thiye saatha haru khaasa
feri vetaula katai.....
Aaja nahula kohi majha
Tara mann ma chau sabai
Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
siir uthaunu ruda ni

Diyo jhai timi ujyaalo charera
baa aama roye ni afno sahara jalera
thulo manche bannu hai vanthye
timi amar vayeu ni niswartha ladai ladera
feri yo bajrapath kasaima naparos hai
kasaiko sahara aago ma dadaunu naparos hai
eutai binti ki sunchau saba?
kathghara ma nyaya paincha ki aba?

Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
siir uthaunu ruda ni

Awaz mera gunjiye ki
mai mari jana le.......


¬©Sushant Ghimire 2025

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion üèÜüî• Live Reaction üò≥
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fire‚Äôs history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And let‚Äôs not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today

snippet.title: Wakka Lagdo Sansar - bekcha - Jodi No.1 Title Song [Lyrical Video]
snippet.description:
#wakkalagdosansar #Jodino1 #bekcha 
Wakka Lagdo Sansar is the original soundtrack for an amazing web series Jodi No. 1 made with love, soul and perseverance by brilliant human beings with big dreams. When you have the time and mind, go catch it here:

The first episode: https://youtu.be/lCakw0IyOt4
Full Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@UC3uDjw2Sg4EgPfZeAR_Q2rQ 

I would like to pay respects to the brave fighters, martyrs of the current movement in Nepal. The whole nation mourns this massive loss and is forever indebted to all of  you.  I am sending out prayers to the bereaved family and friends.

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

Audio Credits:
(Produced, Mixed and Mastered by) https://www.instagram.com/begendra_official
https://www.instagram.com/anmolz_music
Guitars: https://www.instagram.com/bishalchhetriguitar/
Sansic Productions

i'm in instagram sometimes - https://www.instagram.com/b3kcha
and mail me here, if you feel it should get to me: songsbybekcha@gmail.com
